> Texas Chirinos 2-run homer leads Rangers over Blue Jays 5-3 Toronto Blue Jays fans watch during the ninth inning of Game 1 of the American League Division Series against the Texas Rangers in Toronto on Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015.
